flowchart TD
  START([collect componentId + report]) --> ID{componentId present?}
  ID -->|no| VERR[throw ObservabilityValidationError]
  ID -->|yes| LOCK[lock per component]
  LOCK --> UP{component exists?}
  UP -->|yes| MERGE[rehydrate + report merge\ncounters ADD · gauges SET · timers accumulate]
  UP -->|no| NEW[create component service]
  NEW --> MERGE
  MERGE --> STORE[store model · recompute checksum]
  STORE --> EXPORT[provider.exportMetrics]
  EXPORT --> EV1[MetricsCollected]
  EV1 --> HC{health changed?}
  HC -->|yes| EV2[HealthChanged]
  HC -->|no| DONE1([component updated])
  EV2 --> DONE1

  subgraph SNAP[snapshot]
    S1[gather namespace components] --> S2[aggregateMetrics\ncounters/gauges sum · timers merge]
    S2 --> S3[aggregateHealth worst-of]
    S3 --> S4[build snapshot + checksum]
    S4 --> S5[provider.putSnapshot · history ring · SnapshotCreated]
  end

  subgraph DIAG[diagnostics]
    D1[gather components] --> D2[redact sensitive metadata]
    D2 --> D3[failure aggregation\ndegraded + failed]
    D3 --> D4[engine diagnostics + DiagnosticsGenerated]
  end

  subgraph VER[verify]
    V1[recompute component checksums] --> V2[recompute snapshot checksums]
    V2 --> V3[issues[] + VerificationCompleted]
  end

  DONE1 -.-> SNAP
  DONE1 -.-> DIAG
  DONE1 -.-> VER
